metadata.name: Mubadala NFT Stamp 001/500 ● H5scrz
metadata.description: The stamp depicts a painting of key landmarks across Abu Dhabi including Mubadala Tower, the Aldar building, Yas Marina Circuit, in addition to cultural sites such as Louvre Abu Dhabi and Qasr Al Hosn. Each of these landmarks contribute to Abu Dhabi’s economic diversification.The word ‘Abu Dhabi’ can be seen written in Arabic calligraphy above Qasr Al Hosn, showcasing the Emirate’s journey through the progress of the major landmarks featured here.
